		<p class="comment-meta"> 
			<time class="comment-published" datetime="2008-12-01T21:53:49+00:00" title="Monday, December 1, 2008, 9:53 pm" itemprop="commentTime"><a href="http://www.createdinbirmingham.com/2008/12/01/thoughts-on-the-creative-city-awards-2008/#comment-42058">December 1, 2008 at 9:53 pm</a></time>
