		<div class="comment-content">
			<p>As a creative living in this city I wanted to enter these awards but couldn&#8217;t. I didn&#8217;t fit into any category, either financially (I haven&#8217;t made enough money yet) or because I&#8217;ve been in business for longer than 12 months (according to the rules that means I&#8217;m not a new comer).</p>
