<p>CiB awards sounds a little bit worrying to me &#8211; this site works because it doesn&#8217;t put one thing above another qualitatively. Recency and interestingness are the things I look for here. But Pete&#8217;s idea s worth discussing!</p>
<p>There&#8217;s been various conversations for a few years on &#8220;why don&#8217;t we organise a big party every year&#8221; which would seem pretty simple to get off the ground with a few sponsors. Perhaps I&#8217;m naive.</p>
